name: C93 Check the analytics of the folder with 1 downloads and 1 file using the context menu
fullName: C93 Check the analytics of the folder with 1 downloads and 1 file using the context menu

steps.name: Given User should be on the Home web page
And User should be on the Main web page and signed as owner
Given user must be in the "Files" section
And the main folder with any exist files
log _> FOLDER: [cyA.National Operations Developer] ~ created is Successful
assert [Check response status code is 201]: expected **201** to equal **201**
uncaught exception TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'constructor')
And user selects this item and downloads it using Topbar
uncaught exception TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'type')
When user clicks "Analytics" in the context menu of the target "Folder"
Then user should see the "folder" name in the modal form "Analytics folder"
And user should see the 1 number of downloads to the item in the modal form "Analytics folder"
And user should see the 1 number of files containing the folder in the modal form "Analytics folder"
